n
t(r)=\max\{|p(z)|:|z|=r\}
t(r)\geq t(s)
0<r<s
p(z)=z^n
p(z) = a_n z^n + a_{n-1}z^{n-1} + \cdots + a_0
t(r) = \max \limits _{|z| = r} \displaystyle \Bigg| \frac{p(z)}{z^n} \Bigg |
t(r) \gt |a_n|
t(r) = t(s)
r \lt s
R > s > r
t(R) < t(s)
\displaystyle \frac{p(z)}{z^n}
r |\le |z| \le R
|z| = r
|z| = s
\displaystyle \frac{p(z)}{z^n}
t(R) < t(r)
t(s) = t(r)
\displaystyle \frac{p(z)}{z^n} = K
z \to \infty
K = a_n
